Note:
Runa Security Library: Permissions and Access Control Module

Production-ready access control system surpassing enterprise frameworks like
Spring Security, .NET's Authorization, and AWS IAM. Provides fine-grained
permissions, role-based access control (RBAC), attribute-based access control
(ABAC), and policy-based authorization with high performance and scalability.

Features:
- Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) with hierarchical roles
- Attribute-Based Access Control (ABAC) with dynamic policies
- Policy-Based Access Control (PBAC) with rule engines
- Fine-grained permissions with resource-level controls
- Time-based and context-aware access controls
- Dynamic permission evaluation with caching
- Multi-tenant permission isolation
- Delegation and impersonation capabilities
- Permission auditing and compliance tracking
- High-performance permission checking with sub-millisecond response
:End Note

Import "../../datetime" as DateTime
Import "../../collections" as Collections
